   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "### 单元测试、模块测试、集成测试"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "id": "b0a0ab47-16c0-4614-a6ad-4a4f9527f84e",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "> 我现在的感觉，对于一个复杂功能，先独立地实现功能，做单元测试，测试稳定后再集成到系统中；\n",
    "- 单元测试 → Unit Testing / Unit Test\n",
    "- 模块测试 → Module Testing 或更常见写法 Component Testing\n",
    "- 集成测试 → Integration Testing / Integration Test"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "id": "122b5b10-4008-44dd-81bd-b53aeff314ff",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
